objects.name: ControlsText
objects.string:
Controls:
Movement: WASD
Open Inventory: E
Close Inventory: E or Escape
Open Shop (When infront of shop): E
Close Shop: Escape
Manage Inventory: Click and drag on items
Swing Sword: Click with sword in hand
Aim Gun: Hold right click
Shoot Gun: Left click while aiming gun
Plant Seeds: Left click on farm plot with seeds in hand
Harvest Seeds: Left click on finished crop
Go To Main Menu: Escape (when not in shop)
Open Cheats Menu (if enabled in settings): C
Show Stats in Game: P

objects.name: AimText
objects.string:
Aim:
Earn money to buy upgrades
Beat the bosses in caves every 10 levels
Earn Achievements

objects.string:

If you havent already tried your hand at farming, you can restart and try that!

Thanks for playing this short demo!

eventsFunctionsExtensions.author: Gustavo Marciano
eventsFunctionsExtensions.description:
Set the depth (Z-order) of the instance to the value of its Y position in the scene, creating an illusion of depth. The origin point of the object is used to determine the Z-order.

Useful for isometric games, 2D games with a "Top-Down" view, RPG...
eventsFunctionsExtensions.name: YSort
eventsFunctionsExtensions.shortDescription: Create an illusion of depth by setting the Z-order based on the Y position of the object. Useful for isometric games, 2D games with a "Top-Down" view, RPG...
